text:
<!channel>: there are now two distinct versions of the Jordan app.    
MJ = Dev server that we have been using all along
Team Jordan = official Production server - nobody at uncorked should be posting content on this
Team Jordan builds prior to 1.0.46 are fine - but as as of this morning, all new Team Jordan builds are hitting production
as such - you all just got a new build this morning for MJ instead - feel free to continue testing and posting using this MJ build
